lead_paragraph: Stephen Curry scored 25 of his 51 points in the first quarter and sank 11 three-pointers as the Golden State Warriors downed the Washington Wizards 134-121 for their eighth straight win on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Red-Hot Curry Helps Warriors Run Through Wizards
